               <p>The morning that the pots were missing, they were brought to me (deposed to) they were taken from the prisoner.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I had been out of business a great while, and in great distress, I had a wife and child almost starving for bread; I never was guilty of anything before.</p>
